pd_0_com_0text: Thank you for showing my way out! I will be forever in debt with you... How can I reward you?
pd_1_com_0text: You've got a nice sword there...
pd_1_com_1text:
Don't worry about it, I am sure we will meet again. 
Good luck my friend.
pd_2_com_0text:
It's a beauty ain't it? If I have to lose it, I'm glad it falls in worthy hands.
I am sure it will serve you well!
pd_3_com_0text: You are truly a hero! When the time comes, I'll surely repay my debt somehow!
